title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 8 2022

description:
OutKick obtains more maskless Stacey Abrams pics. She was maskless at the school for much more than just that absurd photo op, Clay notes. Adam Soos, Canadian journalist for Rebel News, joins Clay and Buck with the very latest on the trucker convoy protest. Chief teachers union commissar Randi Weingarten: Mask kids until there's zero covid transmission. C&B take calls.
